econd Load Balancer (HAProxy): The second load balancer is added to create a cluster with the first one for redundancy and scalability.

Web Server (Nginx):The web server is added to separate static content serving from dynamic content processing, enhancing scalability and performance.

Application Server:The application server is added to host and execute the application logic, ensuring efficient processing of dynamic requests.

Database Server (MySQL):The database server is added to store and manage application data separately, ensuring data integrity, scalability, and performance.

